{"tid":2421056,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[遊記] 獨遊箱根、新潟越後妻有大地藝術祭","createTime":"2021-02-24T09:05:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T05:51:55.000Z","uid":3560,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5084f432cc867211b4fb27e464fa3d1f16585f50","tid":2421056,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T09:05:46.000Z","msg":"無得去旅行好耐，唯有打遊記止癮<br />\n紀錄2018年夏天一個藝術祭遊記。<br />\n<br />\n先上圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w6CTBmm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw6CTBmm.jpg&h=8e97500d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UaP3d7Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUaP3d7Y.jpg&h=70b5841e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SdFJYzH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSdFJYzH.jpg&h=f1d384bc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UQXsFN2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUQXsFN2.jpg&h=3da11cae&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/88RdBmj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F88RdBmj.jpg&h=d64efc2c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gokFgmj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgokFgmj.jpg&h=2d2c4079&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p9HsFN1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp9HsFN1.jpg&h=a201e937&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DX1w7s1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDX1w7s1.jpg&h=0cd12087&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Fk2uGn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Fk2uGn.jpg&h=445ad2f7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a4VJYzH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa4VJYzH.jpg&h=bef9de28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rm6APGm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frm6APGm.jpg&h=b3bb7137&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n十天行程<br />\nDay 1-5 箱根<br />\nDay 5-6 東京<br />\nDay 6-9 新潟<br />\nDay 10 東京+回程<br />\n<br />\n之前寫過瀨戶內海藝術祭遊記：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1135131\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1135131</a><br />\n不過越後妻有大地藝術祭其實先係我人生第一次參與嘅日本藝術祭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望各位鍾意啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/lucky.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c834d728f010019da50c636721ff58242a1b1d7","tid":2421056,"uid":84013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T09:06:47.000Z","msg":"想睇越後淫妻"},{"pid":"7f3a2de6cadb2874151eebf7dab9189cffe248ad","tid":2421056,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T09:10:43.000Z","msg":"基本資訊<br />\n<br />\n交通：<br />\nJR、火車、巴士、Local Tour<br />\n可惜小妹唔識揸車，唔係應該好玩好多<br />\n<br />\n住宿：<br />\n箱根住強羅溫泉Hostel<br />\n越後妻有住十日町商務旅館<br />\n十日町本身不是旅遊區，本身酒店都唔多間，藝術祭期間嘅住宿就變得非常緊絀，而且大部分民宿經營者連網都唔識上，我最後係Fax去訂宿，非常黐線。<br />\n<br />\nDay 5-6 突然返東京因爲遇上超強颱風，突然改行程避難，臨時Book咗一晚First Cabin。非常滿意，可惜已經執咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c7ac5ae195eb145463befd6ef729d4a4eaec9e2","tid":2421056,"uid":168703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T09:23:38.000Z","msg":"想睇！推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fd410f1b5d3b8f6ff4323abd2540f5cae35f73a","tid":2421056,"uid":3560,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T09:42:37.000Z","msg":"Day 1<br />\n香港凌晨機飛東京成田<br />\n朝早7點半到着<br />\n最愛凌晨機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又好瞓，又慳返一日<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7s9yBu6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7s9yBu6.jpg&h=f3ad21f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kHJWzgN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkHJWzgN.jpg&h=1f7afc0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後就直奔箱根強羅<br />\n成田 Narita Nex --&gt; 新宿 --&gt; 新宿浪漫特急 --&gt; 箱根登山火車<br />\n下晝一點幾就到咗啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n箱根登山火車其實真係好靚<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ytx00Zd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYtx00Zd.jpg&h=77accd90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M6Hwocz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM6Hwocz.jpg&h=9d85e83a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到咗就去到Hostel放低行李<br />\n是次住Hakone Tent 10人Dorm，訓Tatami<br />\n呢間至今都係我住過最最最最好嘅Hostel體驗，超級強推！<br />\n之後再詳細講。<br />\n<br />\n食個快Lunch，就去搭強羅纜車同吊車，直奔大涌谷<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z1Erb7J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz1Erb7J.jpg&h=9e98650d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LeiGLsK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLeiGLsK.jpg&h=5ef92739&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zMKnuUp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzMKnuUp.jpg&h=50e15966&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oCCMb7J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoCCMb7J.jpg&h=f28ee4f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gKPe5sK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgKPe5sK.jpg&h=c811b798&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n強烈嘅硫磺味傳入我個鼻，係溫泉嘅味道啊！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到吊車尾站開始落雨，天色亦開始暗<br />\n唯有放棄海盜船同箱根神社<br />\n俾自己一個藉口再嚟過啦（都唔知幾時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n最後返去早雲山站，見到一間流動咖啡店<br />\n坐低飲杯啡，同店主一路傾偈到日落<br />\n傾下旅行，傾下香港，傾下日本，仲互相交換埋IG<br />\n獨遊遇見嘅人，真係旅行最珍貴嘅回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S9uuUom.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS9uuUom.jpg&h=2aad031f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EjTfPWG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEjTfPWG.jpg&h=af6bcd37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你好，箱根！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q36k01Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq36k01Y.jpg&h=0b5c5bd6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c899c6493ee97abc0ef403e8dd33d3c28e674b85","tid":2421056,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c7ac5ae195eb145463befd6ef729d4a4eaec9e2","tid":2421056,"uid":168703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T09:23:38.000Z","msg":"想睇！推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T09:43:14.000Z","msg":"多謝你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e155e06604ee984756fad1a14d0cee7d0e47dd9e","tid":2421056,"uid":197561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T09:44:13.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"e413967a139c2d062a55402e8495693010569e7d","tid":2421056,"uid":3560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T10:06:30.000Z","msg":"想寫一寫關於強羅嘅Hostel，Hakone Tent <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢一間Hostel係我咁多次獨遊、住咁多次Hostel入面住得最開心嘅一間Hostel<br />\n入面識嘅朋友亦成到而家都仍然有保持聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n我喺Hostel期間無影相，所以補上佢哋Facebook同官網圖片，希望大家唔好介意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n箱根最出名係溫泉旅館，郁下就成千蚊晚<br />\n我呢啲獨遊窮撚住唔起，亦無需要住<br />\n喺強羅車站搵到間有Dorm嘅溫泉Hostel，住Dorm只係3500 Yen一晚，簡直係清泉<br />\n<img src=\"https://travelwerke.files.wordpress.com/2019/04/hakonetent_exterior01.jpg?w=638&amp;h=288\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftravelwerke.files.wordpress.com%2F2019%2F04%2Fhakonetent_exterior01.jpg%3Fw%3D638%26h%3D288&h=70368acd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/proxy/VZRwVgUbZgQRYjqZTExd_mzR-5WFFCzM7C1hKDPA8mB1RqYojiqbPOwo-kHQDmiWBGMwhLsJmOE2CGCs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2Fproxy%2FVZRwVgUbZgQRYjqZTExd_mzR-5WFFCzM7C1hKDPA8mB1RqYojiqbPOwo-kHQDmiWBGMwhLsJmOE2CGCs&h=d1018920&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCheck-in時有個男仔幫我登記，見我係香港人突然轉channel同我講國語<br />\n我極驚訝：「欸，你的中文這麼好！」<br />\n男職員：「我臺灣人，我們有位同事是香港人呢，都是Working Holiday」<br />\n然後我仲遇到來自唔同地方working holiday嘅朋友，亦同我分享咗好多生活點滴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n夜晚強羅呢啲鄉郊地方基本無嘢食<br />\nHostel有個小廚房有西餐同日本餐點可以叫<br />\n價錢亦唔貴，坐低飲杯梅酒食個飯，同Hostel其他人傾下計<br />\n老細亦會彈下結他咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://ik.imagekit.io/tvlk/apr-asset/TzEv3ZUmG4-4Dz22hvmO9NUDzw1DGCIdWl4oPtKumOg=/hotels/15000000/14700000/14696000/14695972/83ec20ed_z.jpg?tr=q-40,c-at_max,w-740,h-500&amp;_src=imagekit\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fik.imagekit.io%2Ftvlk%2Fapr-asset%2FTzEv3ZUmG4-4Dz22hvmO9NUDzw1DGCIdWl4oPtKumOg%3D%2Fhotels%2F15000000%2F14700000%2F14696000%2F14695972%2F83ec20ed_z.jpg%3Ftr%3Dq-40%2Cc-at_max%2Cw-740%2Ch-500%26_src%3Dimagekit&h=4523f1b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嚟到溫泉鄉箱根當然要浸溫泉<br />\n而最犀利嘅地方，我俾3500 yen一晚都有得浸，仲要係半私人風呂形式<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jalan.jp/jalan/images/pict2L/Y8/Y327758/Y327758022.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.jalan.jp%2Fjalan%2Fimages%2Fpict2L%2FY8%2FY327758%2FY327758022.jpg&h=03a43346&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nHostel中有兩個溫泉池，直接用大涌谷溫泉水<br />\n每次只限一組住客入去浸，你入咗去浸之後亦可以鎖門<br />\n嗰半個鐘個溫泉池就變咗你嘅私人風呂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算係唔習慣同陌生人一齊沖涼嘅鬼佬都好享受溫泉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n溫泉要輪流，等嘅期間亦可以喺Bar飲杯酒，玩下Board Game<br />\n強羅極多富士山登山者，大家亦都可以交流下唔同嘅故事，或者甚至係搵旅伴<br />\n大家旅行一日後，返黎食飯玩Game，浸溫泉，交換下相，講下聽日行程<br />\n出門前一齊食早餐，提下今日會凍會落雨着多件衫<br />\n都真係好窩心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：非打手，我都想做到佢哋打手<br />\n一路打都覺得好感動好掛住！<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af7bb19558ea91028fe79f1a365487e345e1dea1","tid":2421056,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e155e06604ee984756fad1a14d0cee7d0e47dd9e","tid":2421056,"uid":197561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T09:44:13.000Z","msg":"留名"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T10:07:01.000Z","msg":"你個名 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n轟啊轟轟轟"},{"pid":"9fd85cc8aee592db6296ef1c189e79bf5a20eb35","tid":2421056,"uid":7311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T10:09:15.000Z","msg":"幾有興趣去啲藝術祭<br />\n<br />\n不過已經諗定有得去日本下次就玩秋田/青森再上北海道<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d8d7585273cb082bf3c0fd3747c973bb2fbaf8d","tid":2421056,"uid":197561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af7bb19558ea91028fe79f1a365487e345e1dea1","tid":2421056,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e155e06604ee984756fad1a14d0cee7d0e47dd9e","tid":2421056,"uid":197561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T09:44:13.000Z","msg":"留名"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T10:07:01.000Z","msg":"你個名 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n轟啊轟轟轟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T10:12:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一齊睇樓主分享"},{"pid":"b12c927dc0bcf1d5370a631b3bf2617301d3d95c","tid":2421056,"uid":56733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T10:17:40.000Z","msg":"樓主啲相係digital or film?"},{"pid":"9637e68dc721a57009950c5e45bb3c9696ab5a02","tid":2421056,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fd85cc8aee592db6296ef1c189e79bf5a20eb35","tid":2421056,"uid":7311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T10:09:15.000Z","msg":"幾有興趣去啲藝術祭<br />\n<br />\n不過已經諗定有得去日本下次就玩秋田/青森再上北海道<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces