d63e1925d30d3647d982761b16aa1a01dd3803","tid":2421056,"uid":28770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T10:22:42.000Z","msg":"我都有去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rgXXi3M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrgXXi3M.png&h=207e032a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T10:23:57.000Z","msg":"清津峽真係靚到仆街<br />\n你自駕定跟團？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T10:24:58.000Z","msg":"早一日跟團撞到3香港人，之後我哋去夾坐的士上去lol"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T10:33:29.000Z","msg":"唔怪得張相可以影到咁少人<br />\n自己夾的士好爽<br />\n跟團趕到仆街又多人"},{"pid":"f7836687e374fae07ba173cf825a8101fb4c977d","tid":2421056,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:53:01.000Z","msg":"DAY 3<br />\n<br />\n景點一：箱根湿生花園！<br />\n<br />\nHostel喺強羅車站隔離<br />\n係登山火車、登山巴士同纜車總站<br />\n是日全日巴士遊，直撘上仙石原，湿生花園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n順帶一提，Hakone Pass交通入場全包，非常抵玩方便 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1hwUmwv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1hwUmwv.jpg&h=b448b8ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1A201Bm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1A201Bm.jpg&h=efbfcd5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4m4rcH2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4m4rcH2.jpg&h=87086972&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GaZVQuJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGaZVQuJ.jpg&h=b057faf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n密集恐懼症慎入<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n湿生花園係植物公園<br />\n我去嗰陣夏天花期過咗，秋天芒草未開，仲要落雨<br />\n大片大片綠色草園仍然好靚<br />\n秋天就有芒草（網上圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zp0mL38.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzp0mL38.jpg&h=9d691f48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下晝天氣開始轉差，越來越大霧，能見度極低<br />\n本身只打算去箱根睇風景、無打算去美術館嘅我<br />\n都要去搵個室內地方避<br />\n結果去咗最近嘅POLA美術館<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2TYWz4p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2TYWz4p.jpg&h=1884d403&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\"><span class=\"orange\">而POLA美術館另我喜出望外！！！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先策展真係佈得超好<br />\n美術館鎮館館藏係莫奈嘅Lily Pond同Cathedral<br />\n但策展放咗好多本地日本現代美術家同漫畫老師嘅作品回應莫奈嘅印象派嘅作品<br />\n反而更突顯時代同突破，而且成件事即刻變得light-hearted同年輕<br />\n地牢就放咗個本地實體化Lily Pond嘅裝置藝術作品<br />\n成個體驗超正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KQ15to9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKQ15to9.jpg&h=bf6828c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（館內只准喺地牢攝影）<br />\n<br />\n而POLA依山而建，室外保留咗森林，興建咗步道<br />\n天氣好仲會睇到動物<br />\n而森林入面亦放咗好多雕塑作品<br />\n變相做咗Sculpture Park<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K0OvEwP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK0OvEwP.jpg&h=b151b4e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZGcz6bQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZGcz6bQ.jpg&h=adc92ea7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vM1ExRN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvM1ExRN.jpg&h=100c0e7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2M9ZxRO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2M9ZxRO.jpg&h=bfb130fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我去嗰日真係好大霧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本身POLA美術館嘅建築已經好靚好有心思<br />\n展覽、作品同體驗都極好<br />\n四季亦都有唔同嘅體驗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n補充網上資料<br />\n一個建築，美術、旅遊、保育、自然<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EDVemMX.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEDVemMX.gif&h=fb801144&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zn4CjyD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZn4CjyD.jpg&h=3b002c85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDAY 3 待續"},{"pid":"0e40818f03dcae8ecc12fc7f5f0d116154cd219e","tid":2421056,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T16:54:05.000Z","msg":"有人睇再繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92fccbd62493e78c4f42067ad61220d832346321","tid":2421056,"uid":28193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5084f432cc867211b4fb27e464fa3d1f16585f50","tid":2421056,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T09:05:46.000Z","msg":"無得去旅行好耐，唯有打遊記止癮<br />\n紀錄2018年夏天一個藝術祭遊記。<br />\n<br />\n先上圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w6CTBmm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw6CTBmm.jpg&h=8e97500d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UaP3d7Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUaP3d7Y.jpg&h=70b5841e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SdFJYzH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http